    <main class="container">
        <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p>Last Updated: October 19, 2025</p>

        <p>Your privacy is important to us. This Privacy Policy explains how KabaleOnline Services ("we," "us," or "our") collects, uses, and protects your information when you use our platform.</p>

        <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
        <p>We collect information to provide and improve our services. This includes:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Personal Identification Information:</strong> When you register, we collect your name, email address, telephone number, location, and profile picture.</li>
            <li><strong>Service and Job Post Information:</strong> We collect details about the services you offer or the jobs you post, including title, description, category, and budget/price.</li>
            <li><strong>User Communications:</strong> We store messages sent through our one-on-one chat and community group chat features to facilitate communication between users.</li>
            <li><strong>Reviews and Ratings:</strong> We collect reviews and ratings you submit for services to build trust within the community.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <p>Your information is used for the following purposes:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>To Operate the Platform:</strong> To create and manage your account, display your profile, and list your services or job posts.</li>
            <li><strong>To Facilitate Communication:</strong> To enable you to communicate with other users through our messaging system.</li>
            <li><strong>To Improve Our Services:</strong> To understand how users interact with our platform so we can improve the user experience and develop new features.</li>
            <li><strong>To Ensure Safety and Security:</strong> To verify accounts, monitor for fraudulent activity, and enforce our Terms of Service.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>3. How We Share Your Information</h2>
        <p>We only share your information in the following ways:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Publicly on Your Profile:</strong> Your name, profile picture, tagline, bio, location, and the services you offer are publicly visible to other users to facilitate connections. Your email and telephone number are kept private and are not displayed publicly.</li>
            <li><strong>Between Users During a Transaction:</strong> When you contact another user or send a proposal, your name and profile picture are shared with them to identify you.</li>
            <li><strong>For Legal Reasons:</strong> We may share information if required by law or to protect the rights, property, or safety of KabaleOnline Services, our users, or the public.</li>
        </ul>
        <p><strong>We do not sell your personal data to third parties.</strong></p>

        <h2>4. Data Security</h2>
        <p>We are committed to protecting your information. We use industry-standard security measures, including data encryption and secure cloud hosting with Firebase, to safeguard your data against unauthorized access or disclosure.</p>

        <h2>5. Your Rights and Choices</h2>
        <p>You have the right to access and control your personal information. Through your "Edit Profile" and "Manage Services" pages, you can:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Access and update your profile information.</li>
            <li>Edit or delete the services you have listed.</li>
        </ul>
        <p>If you wish to delete your account, please contact us directly at <a href="mailto:help@kabaleonline.com">help@kabaleonline.com</a>.</p>

        <h2>6. Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
        <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new policy on this page and updating the "Last Updated" date. You are advised to review this page periodically for any changes.</p>

        <h2>7. Contact Us</h2>
        <p>If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at <a href="mailto:help@kabaleonline.com">help@kabaleonline.com</a>.</p>
